    <h3>Mission Distinctives:</h3>

    <ol>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Crossway on mission exists to glorify God:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><p>Viewing mission as a central act of worship</p></li>
          <li><p>Participating in the good works which God has prepared in advance for us (Eph 2:10)</p></li>
          <li><p>Equipping and mobilizing all members of Crossway</p></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Making disciples of all peoples:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><p>Reconciling and growing people into the image of Christ (2 Cor. 5:17- 21)</p></li>
