        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Through proclaiming:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><p>Declaring Christ as seen in scripture to all peoples in a way they best understand</p></li>
          <li><p>Relying on the power of the Holy Spirit for the proclamation of the Gospel and  works of the miraculous (1 Cor 2:2-5)</p></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Through living out:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><p>Prayerfully relying on God (1 Thess 5:17, Eph 6:18)</p></li>
          <li><p>Joyfully giving of our hearts, lives, and resources (James 2:14-15)</p></li>
          <li><p>Growing in acts of justice and mercy (Micah 6:8)</p></li>
          <li><p>Emulating Christ's example of servant-like humility in any given context (Phil 2: 3-8)</p></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>The Gospel of Jesus Christ:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><p>"For God so loved the world that He gave His only Son, that whoever believes in Him should not perish but will have everlasting life." John 3:16</p></li>
